{"tid":1910190,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析]北角佛堂義工(確診個案98)曾到觀塘藥房中醫求診  瑞和街599C十面埋伏","createTime":"2020-03-04T13:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T11:12:18.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cbd2eee96924986627f17c7f806a331e1a89a3","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"第98宗確診個案、71歲住藍田康瑞苑女子，她是北角佛堂義工，曾到物華街11號長春中西藥房看中醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>個案 98 : 住院<br />\n香港居民<br />\n女 71 歲<br />\n本地個案的密切接觸者<br />\n01/03/2020 (確診)<br />\n12/02/2020 (發病)<br />\n觀塘 <br />\n物華街11號 (非住宅)<br />\n最後有個案在出現病徵期間逗留的日期:<br />\n26/2/2020</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入住醫院:<br />\n基督教聯合醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2isvG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2isvG9.jpg&h=e1cf664f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n599C已將瑞和街市政大廈重重包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a3f92184f008819f2af2e2a53edbed0c34cd18","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"梁凱晴(月華)都好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V406Mhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV406Mhw.jpg&h=b32b3334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list_detail.php?member_id=2735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkt%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list_detail.php%3Fmember_id%3D2735&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=dab09d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list_detail.php?member_id=2735</a><br />\nbtw 梁凱晴聯絡方式係觀塘和樂邨長安樓地下104室<br />\n<br />\n個度係 <span style=\"color: green;\">民主黨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 胡志偉(九龍東)、鄭景陽(寶樂) 辦事處<br />\n怕佢比熱狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d60c327ddfd087e5cb295333e714bfd1c78058","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00a3f92184f008819f2af2e2a53edbed0c34cd18","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"梁凱晴(月華)都好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V406Mhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV406Mhw.jpg&h=b32b3334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list_detail.php?member_id=2735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkt%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list_detail.php%3Fmember_id%3D2735&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=dab09d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list_detail.php?member_id=2735</a><br />\nbtw 梁凱晴聯絡方式係觀塘和樂邨長安樓地下104室<br />\n<br />\n個度係 <span style=\"color: green;\">民主黨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 胡志偉(九龍東)、鄭景陽(寶樂) 辦事處<br />\n怕佢比熱狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:25:24.000Z","msg":"<em>由於月華前任區議員屬於房署單位嘅辦公室由謝偉俊獨力續租，而月華街附近缺乏可負擔嘅鋪位。雖然同唔少素人一樣，面對重大困難，但我哋係唔會頹廢；凱晴正式由今個星期開始，每逢星期六朝早同星期日下晝都會喺月華街開設流動辦事處！<br />\n<br />\n街坊FAQ：<br />\nQ1. 點解謝偉俊可以續租？唔係觀塘區議員優先咩？<br />\nA1. 因謝偉俊係原合租人，因此有續租優先權。<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 咁謝偉俊可以租幾耐？<br />\nA2. 理論上佢一日係立法會議員，佢都可以續租落去。<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 點解唔搵鄰近月華嘅工廠區？<br />\nA3. 工業用途單位唔合資格取得區議會租金津貼。<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 點解唔租協和街嘅商鋪？<br />\nA4. 以我哋暫時掌握嘅資料，所有合規格嘅商鋪租金都超出區議會津貼讓我哋可以負擔嘅範圍。<br />\n<br />\nQ5. 咁閒日點樣搵到凱晴團隊？<br />\nA5. 可以打98486284比我哋；同時我哋同鄰近區議員協商緊暫借地方臨時辦公，詳情等我哋遲啲再公布啦！</em>"},{"pid":"e217ed6b146b5f35cf4c978b0d65e1612b8ac155","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:26:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">[多圖]</span>觀塘舊樓單位爆屎渠3天 屎水浸走廊 正面播毒瑞和街市政大廈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863815</a>"},{"pid":"344901caf22c40303f92618d61346085d0734ced","tid":1910190,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"宇清終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f172b582a0e33887a7d8eae79c269a5af69750bd","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"陳梓維議員(佐敦南)選區分析<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WP1JonB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWP1JonB.jpg&h=7a6c19af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳梓維議員中咗胡椒噴霧痛到入院。。。。。。。。。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fehamS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fehamS</a>"},{"pid":"77d3b5f3a358282385d5f6a8a973fd2ca3946cfa","tid":1910190,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344901caf22c40303f92618d61346085d0734ced","tid":1910190,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"宇清終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"入隔離營放針啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d981d8ffa33a070e0256b05a5de12ed3ce1b95d","tid":1910190,"uid":7439,